"30783fe fix for bug #342105:  Close button not shown if there is only one tab per beltzner: "The close button should be shown, with the effect being that it disposes the tab and immediately opens a new one. Strange behaviour surely, but I think it's the easiest and most reliably understandable case." thanks to Simon <zeniko@gmail.com> for the patch. r=sspitzer, sr=mconnor
